        "kind": "pull_request",
        "title": "Add Zed provider using editor Keychain session",
        "body": "## Summary\n\n- Add a Zed provider using the signed-in editor's macOS Keychain credentials.\n- Call `GET /client/users/me` for plan, edit-prediction quota, billing-cycle metadata, and overdue-invoice state.\n- Honor Zed's `~/.config/zed/settings.json` credential/server overrides while requiring HTTPS and same-origin credentials for custom servers.\n- Add provider registration, icon, CLI integration, docs, and focused tests.\n\n## Maintainer rewrite\n\n- Rebased onto current `main`.\n- Removed dashboard-cookie billing, browser import, settings UI, and static token-credit claims; this PR now ships only the native editor session path.\n- Preserved refresh cancellation and classified transport failures correctly.\n- Bound custom-server credentials to the same HTTPS origin so settings cannot forward a Keychain token elsewhere.\n- Removed unused fixtures and updated public provider counts to 53.\n\n## Validation\n\n- `swift test --filter 'ZedStatusProbeTests|ProviderRegistryTests|ConfigurationDocsProviderIDTests|CodexBarWidgetProviderTests|ProviderIconResourcesTests'` (44 tests)\n- `swift test --filter 'ZedStatusProbeTests|CodexLoginRunnerTests'` (20 tests)\n- `CodexLoginRunnerTests` repeated 10 times with `--skip-build`\n- `make check`\n- local uncommitted autoreview: clean, no actionable findings\n- full branch autoreview against `origin/main`: clean, no actionable findings\n- CI-fixture autoreview: clean, no actionable findings\n\n## Exact-head packaged proof\n\n- Head: `8c84fa7632838dcbc0c0a8a520d49d3ec41771f1`\n- Packaged with `CODEXBAR_SIGNING=adhoc ./Scripts/package_app.sh`\n- Packaged CLI SHA-256: `81d3d2b076b2317498787b06cb55354023d0b67d8542f16fb718d5459dd8b7ae`\n- Live signed-in editor Keychain refresh returned `source: local`, no provider error, and empty stderr.\n\n```json\n[\n  {\n    \"provider\": \"zed\",\n    \"source\": \"local\",\n    \"error\": false,\n    \"loginMethod\": \"Zed Free\",\n    \"primaryUsedPercent\": 0,\n    \"primaryResetDescription\": \"0 / 2000 predictions\",\n    \"secondaryResetDescription\": \"Cycle ends in 29d 21h\",\n    \"windowCount\": 2\n  }\n]\n```\n\nAccount identity and credentials were omitted from proof output.\n\nRefs #846.\n",
